channel.title: Bronze full hel G looks weird
channel.description: Hey Guys for some reason my bronze helm G looks weird on my server.. the plate and legs and kite look fine but its just the helm. I went in item.java and put it in the full helm slot but then i still wielded it as a weapon so i put it in the hat slot also.. then i wielded it as a helm but it was shaped weird and everything.. I would be glad if someone could help me :]
